WEBVTT

02:04.870 --> 02:05.950
You're here.

02:06.280 --> 02:07.790
I brought you some snacks.

02:09.400 --> 02:10.190
No need.

02:10.360 --> 02:12.160
I don't have much of an appetite.

02:13.190 --> 02:14.850
Why don't you go back and rest?

02:15.000 --> 02:16.630
You are already so exhausted.

02:16.630 --> 02:18.190
I still have 2 medical books to read.

02:18.190 --> 02:18.800
Tomorrow.

02:27.590 --> 02:29.120
You can read them tomorrow.

02:30.030 --> 02:31.560
You don't need to worry about me.

02:31.560 --> 02:33.030
There's a small bed inside.

02:33.030 --> 02:34.760
I can rest there when I'm tired.

02:35.590 --> 02:37.000
You're a woman.

02:37.079 --> 02:38.030
This won't do.

02:40.190 --> 02:41.840
Why won't it do?

02:41.870 --> 02:43.400
It's really nice.

02:43.840 --> 02:44.960
Let me show you.

02:56.470 --> 02:57.280
Look.

02:58.430 --> 02:59.630
You're sleeping here?

02:59.630 --> 03:00.630
This won't do.

03:01.030 --> 03:02.190
Why not?

03:02.750 --> 03:04.400
Of course, it's not as comfortable
as the mansion,

03:04.400 --> 03:06.530
but it's enough for an occasional nap.

03:08.560 --> 03:09.680
In this case,

03:10.560 --> 03:12.290
I'll stay and keep you company.

03:13.840 --> 03:15.630
You just recovered not long ago.

03:15.630 --> 03:16.630
Pushing yourself like this,

03:16.630 --> 03:18.230
I'm worried you'll relapse.

03:18.430 --> 03:19.800
I'm fine.

03:19.800 --> 03:22.200
This is much better
than the military camp.

03:23.240 --> 03:24.370
Then I won't insist.

03:24.750 --> 03:26.710
If you're tired, rest here for a while.

03:26.710 --> 03:27.240
Okay.

03:32.079 --> 03:33.000
What's wrong?

03:33.360 --> 03:34.690
Are you feeling unwell?

03:36.220 --> 03:36.900
No.

03:36.960 --> 03:38.960
Maybe I haven't rested well
the past couple of days.

03:38.960 --> 03:40.820
I'll be fine after a little sleep.

03:41.079 --> 03:42.400
Are you really okay?

03:42.560 --> 03:43.150
Yes.

03:43.430 --> 03:44.760
Go ahead with your work.

04:53.270 --> 04:55.400
I didn't expect that he still keeps it.

05:13.800 --> 05:14.680
Physician Han.

05:14.800 --> 05:16.270
Something terrible has happened.

05:16.270 --> 05:18.000
His Majesty's condition
has suddenly worsened.

05:18.000 --> 05:19.360
Please go and treat him immediately.

05:19.360 --> 05:20.070
What?

05:20.160 --> 05:21.070
How could this be?

05:21.070 --> 05:22.070
I don't know.

05:22.070 --> 05:23.130
I'll go right away.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.000
I'll go with you.

05:24.000 --> 05:24.480
Okay.

05:30.800 --> 05:31.630
His Majesty has not had any food

05:31.630 --> 05:32.630
or water for days.

05:32.830 --> 05:33.950
If this continues,

05:33.950 --> 05:35.600
how can his body endure it?

05:35.830 --> 05:37.630
We've tried every possible method,

05:37.630 --> 05:39.480
but the results have been very limited.

05:39.480 --> 05:40.430
What should we do?

05:40.430 --> 05:41.720
Indeed.

05:42.270 --> 05:43.360
Prescribe some more tonics.

05:43.360 --> 05:43.830
Okay.

05:43.830 --> 05:45.960
Let me check His Majesty's condition.

06:04.560 --> 06:05.160
How is it?

06:05.560 --> 06:07.270
His Majesty's pulse is weak.

06:07.270 --> 06:08.240
We must find the cause

06:08.240 --> 06:10.370
of his nightmares as soon as possible.

06:39.190 --> 06:39.720
This is...

06:39.720 --> 06:40.780
Don't come closer.

06:43.800 --> 06:44.860
I need to cut it out.

06:45.430 --> 06:46.040
Cut?

06:47.390 --> 06:48.070
Physician Han,

06:48.070 --> 06:48.800
you can't do this.

06:48.800 --> 06:50.000
How can you use a knife

06:50.000 --> 06:50.680
on His Majesty's body?

06:50.680 --> 06:52.070
Please think twice, Physician Han.

06:52.070 --> 06:53.400
If anything goes wrong,

06:53.560 --> 06:55.420
I will bear full responsibility.

07:24.800 --> 07:25.630
Look...

07:25.630 --> 07:26.750
What is it?

07:26.750 --> 07:28.070
Right, worms.

07:33.630 --> 07:34.870
Jin Xi.

07:37.310 --> 07:38.600
Jin Xi!

07:45.630 --> 07:46.630
Your Highness.

07:46.830 --> 07:48.560
Jin Xi didn't enter the palace.

07:50.240 --> 07:51.040
Your Highness.

07:51.040 --> 07:52.830
Even if you don't consider yourself,

07:52.830 --> 07:55.070
you must consider the child
you're carrying.

07:55.070 --> 07:55.920
The floor is cold.

07:55.920 --> 07:56.920
Let me help you up.

08:03.070 --> 08:04.680
Is His Majesty better?

08:05.000 --> 08:06.240
There is no news yet.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.830
There are still many guards

08:07.830 --> 08:09.890
outside our Noble Consort Pavilion.

08:32.669 --> 08:34.030
Help me send this out.

08:34.080 --> 08:35.210
Find Physician Han.

08:36.750 --> 08:37.750
Find Lord Fei

08:38.080 --> 08:39.870
and tell him he must come see me.

08:54.840 --> 08:57.390
Did I really harm Liu Chu?

09:01.200 --> 09:03.240
That's too reckless.

09:03.440 --> 09:05.200
If anything happens to His Majesty,

09:05.200 --> 09:07.240
your entire family will be executed.

09:07.240 --> 09:08.840
My family is already gone.

09:08.840 --> 09:10.150
The situation was urgent.

09:10.150 --> 09:11.240
If we don't treat
His Majesty immediately,

09:11.240 --> 09:12.390
he will be in danger.

09:12.440 --> 09:14.150
And you, General Xiao.

09:14.150 --> 09:16.240
Holding a weapon in the hall

09:16.240 --> 09:18.480
is a crime of profound disrespect.

09:19.750 --> 09:22.360
The Eldest Princess has arrived.

09:22.600 --> 09:24.270
Greetings, Your Highness.

09:24.270 --> 09:26.480
Greetings, Your Highness.

09:27.390 --> 09:28.550
You may all rise.

09:29.030 --> 09:30.150
What happened?

09:30.480 --> 09:33.270
Physician Han and General Xiao
are harming the Emperor's body,

09:33.270 --> 09:35.800
showing profound disrespect
to His Majesty.

09:35.960 --> 09:37.150
Your Highness,

09:37.240 --> 09:38.840
His Majesty was poisoned by Gu.

09:38.840 --> 09:39.600
That is why

09:39.600 --> 09:41.480
the cause of his illness
couldn't be found.

09:41.480 --> 09:43.030
Now that the Gu worm has been removed,

09:43.030 --> 09:44.240
please rest assured.

09:46.480 --> 09:48.390
If, as Physician Han said,

09:48.390 --> 09:49.750
you and General Xiao did this

09:49.750 --> 09:51.270
to save His Majesty,

09:51.480 --> 09:53.840
then naturally I will not
pursue the matter.

09:53.840 --> 09:55.300
Thank you, Your Highness.

09:55.510 --> 09:56.910
No need for formalities.

09:57.150 --> 09:58.630
The top priority now

09:58.630 --> 10:00.750
is to wake His Majesty
up as soon as possible.

10:00.750 --> 10:02.280
I will certainly do my best.

10:04.750 --> 10:05.870
That explains

10:06.080 --> 10:08.150
why we couldn't diagnose
His Majesty's illness all this time.

10:08.150 --> 10:09.840
it turns out he was poisoned by Gu.

10:09.840 --> 10:10.600
Well,

10:10.720 --> 10:12.390
why do you seem relieved?

10:12.840 --> 10:14.240
You don't know this.

10:14.670 --> 10:16.360
Uncle Lie has done a lot of research

10:16.360 --> 10:17.390
on the Gu poison of Changmo.

10:17.390 --> 10:18.870
He previously developed

10:18.870 --> 10:20.240
a special pill

10:20.240 --> 10:22.300
that can be used to ward off Gu poison.

10:23.270 --> 10:24.440
Then Chu is saved.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.480
Exactly.

10:30.480 --> 10:32.410
May the ancestors of Changmo bless

10:33.790 --> 10:35.440
Liu Chu to wake up safely.

10:36.200 --> 10:37.860
If we can survive this ordeal,

10:39.550 --> 10:41.680
I am willing to spend the rest of my life

10:43.030 --> 10:45.240
in exchange for his well-being

10:45.670 --> 10:47.670
and peace between the two lands.

10:53.150 --> 10:54.080
Your Highness,

10:54.240 --> 10:55.270
Lord Fei is here.

10:57.670 --> 10:59.070
Please ask him to come in.

11:09.030 --> 11:09.890
Your Highness,

11:10.000 --> 11:11.000
you summoned me.

11:11.000 --> 11:11.790
Lord Fei,

11:12.870 --> 11:14.200
how is Liu Chu?

11:17.030 --> 11:18.830
His condition is still the same.

11:19.000 --> 11:20.600
He still hasn't woken up.

11:21.240 --> 11:22.870
General Xiao and Physician Han

11:22.870 --> 11:24.470
have been trying their best.

11:26.030 --> 11:26.870
That's good.

11:27.480 --> 11:29.340
Physician Han is highly skilled.

11:29.670 --> 11:31.440
She has many good remedies.

11:31.960 --> 11:33.760
She can definitely save Liu Chu.

11:34.480 --> 11:36.610
Is there anything else I can do for him?

11:38.600 --> 11:39.460
Your Highness,

11:39.720 --> 11:40.550
all you can do now

11:40.550 --> 11:43.150
is take care of yourself
and your unborn child.

11:43.870 --> 11:45.670
Please don't worry too much

11:46.080 --> 11:47.680
and harm the imperial child.

11:48.670 --> 11:49.600
I know.

11:50.240 --> 11:51.040
Consort Ling,

11:51.630 --> 11:53.160
I shouldn't stay here long,

11:53.360 --> 11:54.620
so I will take my leave.

11:54.790 --> 11:55.750
Please

11:55.960 --> 11:57.960
remember what I just said.

11:58.440 --> 11:59.570
Thank you, Lord Fei.

12:00.240 --> 12:01.370
I will take my leave.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.840
Why are you only here now?

12:14.840 --> 12:16.600
Greetings, Your Highness.

12:22.000 --> 12:23.480
Are you sure this antidote works?

12:23.480 --> 12:24.720
There's no other choice

12:24.720 --> 12:25.790
but to give it a try.

12:26.480 --> 12:28.610
If anything happens to His Majesty...

13:12.960 --> 13:14.600
What's wrong?

13:14.670 --> 13:15.930
What's wrong with him?

13:15.960 --> 13:17.020
Let's wait and see.

13:17.480 --> 13:18.870
Xie.

13:18.870 --> 13:19.720
I'm here.

13:20.000 --> 13:20.480
Xie.

13:20.480 --> 13:21.280
Your Majesty.

13:22.000 --> 13:23.030
I'm here.

13:23.670 --> 13:27.030
Your Majesty.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.150
Liu Chu.

13:28.790 --> 13:29.600
Liu Chu.

13:30.030 --> 13:30.840
Liu Chu.

13:34.840 --> 13:35.870
Your Majesty.

13:39.790 --> 13:40.630
This...

13:43.670 --> 13:45.270
How is that possible?

13:46.030 --> 13:47.000
His Majesty...

13:48.150 --> 13:49.550
His Majesty...

13:51.870 --> 13:53.200
has stopped breathing.

13:54.750 --> 13:55.870
Your Majesty!

13:56.150 --> 13:59.630
Your Majesty!

13:59.630 --> 14:01.320
How is that possible?

14:01.320 --> 14:03.360
Your Majesty!

14:03.360 --> 14:04.480
Your Majesty!

14:04.600 --> 14:06.730
How could you just pass away like this?

14:12.320 --> 14:13.360
What happened?

14:15.600 --> 14:16.440
Enough!

14:17.750 --> 14:18.550
Guards!

14:18.840 --> 14:20.440
Take Han Yunling and Xiao Chi

14:20.440 --> 14:21.670
to the Imperial Prison.

14:21.670 --> 14:22.440
Yes.

14:24.960 --> 14:25.960
Move.

14:38.030 --> 14:39.240
Pass my order.

14:40.240 --> 14:42.360
Close the palace gates from today.

14:42.870 --> 14:44.440
No one is allowed to leave.

14:44.840 --> 14:46.080
If anyone spreads the news

14:46.080 --> 14:47.410
of His Majesty's death,

14:47.480 --> 14:49.480
I will execute their entire family!

14:49.870 --> 14:51.000
Yes.

14:51.000 --> 14:52.000
Get lost!

15:04.600 --> 15:05.630
Your Highness,

15:06.480 --> 15:08.150
His Majesty has passed away.

15:08.670 --> 15:09.960
What should we do?

15:12.440 --> 15:13.480
Your Highness,

15:13.480 --> 15:16.010
you are the only descendant
of the Liu family.

15:16.080 --> 15:18.320
You are now the sole ruler of Jinglan.

15:19.080 --> 15:20.480
At this time,

15:20.910 --> 15:22.840
we cannot be indecisive.

15:22.840 --> 15:23.670
You may leave.

15:26.150 --> 15:26.960
Yes.

15:44.240 --> 15:45.000
Xie.

15:45.870 --> 15:46.670
Xie.

15:47.200 --> 15:48.870
You are smart and wise.

15:49.790 --> 15:53.480
But Liu Chu is innocent and naive.

15:53.960 --> 15:56.750
You must manage the treasury well

15:57.240 --> 15:59.030
and assist Liu Chu.

16:00.440 --> 16:02.750
The kingdom of Jinglan

16:02.750 --> 16:05.270
is now in your hands.

16:05.270 --> 16:05.840
Father.

16:05.840 --> 16:07.870
I will definitely take good care of Chu.

16:07.870 --> 16:09.360
I promise.

16:09.480 --> 16:10.120
Okay.

16:13.720 --> 16:16.240
Father!

16:16.240 --> 16:19.440
Your Majesty!

16:21.240 --> 16:23.030
Is this the will of Heaven?

16:23.440 --> 16:25.030
His Majesty has passed away.

16:25.030 --> 16:27.000
Jinglan will inevitably fall into chaos.

16:27.000 --> 16:29.660
The court ministers
will surely be leaderless—

16:29.840 --> 16:32.170
only you can step forward and take charge.

16:32.550 --> 16:33.480
For Jinglan,

16:33.480 --> 16:34.540
and for the people,

16:34.840 --> 16:36.700
please follow the will of Heaven.

16:40.550 --> 16:42.360
Follow the will of Heaven?

16:45.240 --> 16:49.030
What should we do?

16:49.360 --> 16:50.870
This is so sudden.

16:50.870 --> 16:53.730
The state cannot be
without a ruler for a single day.

16:55.790 --> 16:57.520
What are you all arguing about?

16:59.240 --> 17:01.030
Lord Zhang and Lord Li are here.

17:01.030 --> 17:02.480
Every single one of you

17:02.480 --> 17:04.440
is an important minister of the court.

17:04.440 --> 17:07.349
Making such a racket in this hall—

17:08.240 --> 17:09.680
How inappropriate!

17:11.030 --> 17:11.790
Exactly.

17:12.000 --> 17:13.240
How inappropriate!

17:13.829 --> 17:15.349
In this court,

17:15.510 --> 17:16.960
with Lord Zhang here,

17:16.960 --> 17:18.790
Jinglan will not fall into chaos.

17:18.790 --> 17:20.440
That may be true,

17:20.440 --> 17:22.880
but His Majesty's fate is unknown.

17:23.160 --> 17:24.790
How can we not panic?

17:24.790 --> 17:26.480
Yes, right.

17:50.880 --> 17:53.880
If His Majesty really passes away,

17:53.880 --> 17:56.790
wouldn't Jinglan be left without a leader?

17:56.790 --> 18:00.160
Wouldn't the Liu Family have no successor?

18:00.160 --> 18:02.400
Even if His Majesty passes away,

18:02.400 --> 18:04.270
we have to accept it.

18:04.830 --> 18:06.480
The main question is what we should do.

18:06.480 --> 18:08.030
What should Jinglan do?

18:08.030 --> 18:09.830
Without the Liu Family ruling the world,

18:09.830 --> 18:12.480
could our great Jinglan really perish?

18:12.480 --> 18:14.400
What you said makes sense.

18:14.400 --> 18:15.400
But Liu Chu

18:15.400 --> 18:17.880
doesn't have the ability
to govern Jinglan after all.

18:17.880 --> 18:19.880
It's the same with or without him.

18:19.880 --> 18:21.480
Even if he dies,

18:21.480 --> 18:23.960
aren't Lord Zhang
and Lord Li still there?

18:23.960 --> 18:26.000
Jinglan won't be in chaos.

18:26.270 --> 18:27.110
Yes.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.590
We have Lord Zhang and Lord Li.

18:28.590 --> 18:30.030
Lord Zhang.

18:30.240 --> 18:31.070
Look,

18:31.070 --> 18:34.030
this is what the people want.

18:34.350 --> 18:36.240
Yes, Lord Zhang.

18:36.350 --> 18:38.080
Jinglan cannot do without you.

18:38.160 --> 18:41.030
My fellow ministers,

18:41.030 --> 18:43.240
are you forcing me

18:43.240 --> 18:45.570
to become an eternal traitor to the realm?

18:46.000 --> 18:47.640
Lord Zhang.

18:47.790 --> 18:49.110
The common people

18:49.110 --> 18:52.590
will engrave your achievements
on a monument

18:52.590 --> 18:55.030
for generations to come.

18:55.350 --> 18:57.110
Yes.

18:57.240 --> 18:58.640
I cannot do it!

18:58.640 --> 19:00.240
Lord Zhang, this is
what everyone expects of you.

19:00.240 --> 19:01.030
I cannot do it!

19:01.030 --> 19:01.720
Lord Zhang.

19:02.350 --> 19:02.880
Yes.

19:02.880 --> 19:03.680
I cannot do it!

19:03.920 --> 19:05.070
Lord Zhang.

19:05.790 --> 19:08.390
The Liu Family hasn't
completely died out yet.

19:13.350 --> 19:15.590
You are indeed a member of the Liu Family.

19:15.590 --> 19:18.640
But you are a woman.

19:18.640 --> 19:19.750
Since ancient times,

19:19.750 --> 19:22.440
there has never been a precedent
for a woman to be an emperor.

19:22.440 --> 19:23.160
That's right.

19:23.160 --> 19:25.270
Your Highness
has managed the treasury for many years

19:25.270 --> 19:27.200
and indeed has a talent for finance.

19:27.200 --> 19:28.790
But when it comes to ruling the country

19:28.790 --> 19:30.440
and leading the ministers—

19:30.440 --> 19:31.400
well,

19:31.400 --> 19:33.030
who would truly accept your authority?

19:33.030 --> 19:34.480
Yes.

19:36.550 --> 19:38.830
You were all promoted
by the late emperor

19:38.830 --> 19:41.430
to reach your current positions,
weren't you?

19:41.590 --> 19:42.790
Each one of you has enjoyed
wealth, honor,

19:42.790 --> 19:44.640
and power for years,

19:44.880 --> 19:47.080
yet not a shred of gratitude do you have.

19:49.480 --> 19:50.880
A couple of insolent buffoons,

19:50.880 --> 19:52.200
nobodies,

19:52.200 --> 19:54.440
daring to disrupt
the imperial court's order?

19:54.440 --> 19:55.160
Guards!

19:55.480 --> 19:57.400
Take them away
and execute them on the spot.

19:57.400 --> 19:58.160
Yes!

19:58.160 --> 19:59.110
Lord Zhang.

19:59.400 --> 20:01.030
Lord Zhang, we are innocent! Lord Zhang!

20:01.030 --> 20:01.690
Lord Zhang.

20:01.750 --> 20:02.920
Lord Zhang, we are innocent!

20:02.920 --> 20:04.510
Lord Zhang, we are innocent!

20:04.510 --> 20:05.640
Save us, Lord Zhang.

20:05.640 --> 20:07.040
Who else dares to object?

20:07.510 --> 20:08.880
Lord Zhang!

20:09.510 --> 20:11.030
We are innocent!

20:13.000 --> 20:13.880
Lord Zhang.

20:14.830 --> 20:16.510
I am here.

20:16.790 --> 20:18.590
You are a veteran official.

20:19.030 --> 20:20.960
If your legs and feet are not nimble,

20:20.960 --> 20:23.200
I will have someone
bring a cushion for you

20:23.200 --> 20:25.730
and grant you the honor
of sitting in the hall.

20:26.070 --> 20:27.350
What do you think?

20:28.440 --> 20:29.200
I

20:29.750 --> 20:31.160
thank Your Highness.

20:31.590 --> 20:32.510
Li Shichang.

20:33.790 --> 20:34.790
I am here.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.830
Do you think in this court,

20:37.830 --> 20:39.880
there is anyone other than me, Liu Xie,

20:39.880 --> 20:41.740
more suitable for this position?

20:42.680 --> 20:44.240
Naturally, the Liu Family's empire

20:44.240 --> 20:46.510
should be ruled by the Liu Family.

20:46.510 --> 20:49.030
Your Highness, although you are a woman,

20:49.160 --> 20:50.880
in terms of talent and ability,

20:50.880 --> 20:53.310
you are no less than any man in the court.

20:53.590 --> 20:54.200
If—

20:54.200 --> 20:56.030
and I mean if—

20:56.310 --> 20:58.970
something unfortunate happens
to His Majesty,

20:59.160 --> 21:03.000
you are undeniably the one
to succeed the throne.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.690
What do you think, Lord Zhang?

21:08.000 --> 21:10.480
I have absolutely no objections.

21:10.480 --> 21:11.350
All right.

21:12.550 --> 21:15.440
Since the two Chief Grand Secretaries
both say so,

21:16.750 --> 21:18.920
Then I will not refuse.

21:19.200 --> 21:20.060
Your Highness,

21:20.270 --> 21:21.030
please.

21:38.960 --> 21:41.350
Jinglan cannot be
without a ruler for a day.

21:41.350 --> 21:43.000
His Majesty is currently unwell.

21:43.000 --> 21:44.160
I, Liu Xie,

21:44.160 --> 21:45.640
born into the royal family

21:45.640 --> 21:47.240
and sharing the same blood
with His Majesty,

21:47.240 --> 21:48.590
should shoulder

21:48.590 --> 21:50.480
the responsibility
of maintaining the stability of the state,

21:50.480 --> 21:52.940
to ensure the eternal prosperity
of Jinglan

21:53.030 --> 21:55.360
and the peace and happiness of the people.

21:59.270 --> 22:02.200
With Your Highness
ascending the throne,

22:02.400 --> 22:04.960
Jinglan will surely prosper forever,

22:04.960 --> 22:06.880
and the people will live in peace.

22:13.750 --> 22:15.280
How could the morning court

22:18.030 --> 22:19.750
proceed without me?

22:21.240 --> 22:22.480
Your Majesty.

22:23.160 --> 22:24.640
Your Majesty.

22:25.030 --> 22:26.510
Your Majesty.

23:06.030 --> 23:07.070
You may leave now.

23:07.070 --> 23:07.830
Yes.

23:16.680 --> 23:17.480
Xiao Chi.

23:18.880 --> 23:19.880
Did Chu really...

23:20.200 --> 23:21.070
Chu isn't dead.

23:22.200 --> 23:23.440
After Yunling removed the Gu worms

23:23.440 --> 23:24.350
from his body,

23:24.550 --> 23:26.950
Chu decided
to play along with their trick.

23:29.400 --> 23:30.880
You guys are too bold.

23:31.270 --> 23:32.480
What if something happened to him—

23:32.480 --> 23:33.640
He had planned this

23:33.640 --> 23:34.640
since he fell ill.

23:37.880 --> 23:38.880
I see.

23:40.400 --> 23:42.830
Only by spreading the news
of His Majesty's death

23:42.830 --> 23:44.000
can those with ulterior motives

23:44.000 --> 23:45.330
show their true colors.

23:45.960 --> 23:47.880
Then we can completely
eradicate hidden dangers

23:47.880 --> 23:49.740
and consolidate imperial power.

23:51.000 --> 23:53.350
This is the medicine His Majesty needs
for his recovery.

23:53.350 --> 23:54.950
Please take it out, Lord Fei.

23:57.200 --> 23:58.000
Rest assured.

23:58.240 --> 23:59.070
I'll go right now.

23:59.070 --> 23:59.640
Zheng.

24:00.030 --> 24:01.640
This is a matter of great importance.

24:01.640 --> 24:03.300
The only ones Chu can trust now

24:03.350 --> 24:05.030
are you and me.

24:07.200 --> 24:08.030
I, Fei Zheng,

24:08.790 --> 24:10.920
will make sure he takes this medicine.

24:31.030 --> 24:32.890
Offer the Eldest Princess a seat.

24:37.030 --> 24:37.960
Your Majesty.

24:38.640 --> 24:40.370
Are you going to pass the throne

24:40.640 --> 24:42.880
to the Eldest Princess?

24:43.270 --> 24:43.960
Xie,

24:43.960 --> 24:45.030
Father is going to pass the throne to you.

24:45.030 --> 24:46.030
I do have this idea.

24:46.030 --> 24:47.230
Don't talk nonsense.

24:48.480 --> 24:50.880
She is indeed outstanding.

24:50.880 --> 24:51.880
But Your Majesty,

24:52.680 --> 24:56.000
do you know
what "eating an heirless household" means?

24:56.030 --> 24:57.830
"Eating an heirless household"?

24:57.830 --> 24:58.550
Yes.

24:58.790 --> 25:00.190
Among the common people,

25:00.350 --> 25:02.070
if there is no male in the family

25:02.070 --> 25:03.790
and only women are left,

25:03.880 --> 25:05.240
the family's property

25:05.240 --> 25:06.440
will be divided by other relatives

25:06.440 --> 25:08.880
and villagers in the clan.

25:09.030 --> 25:11.160
Your Majesty, you have a prince,

25:11.160 --> 25:13.750
but you intend to pass
the throne to the Princess.

25:13.750 --> 25:14.880
First,

25:15.030 --> 25:16.790
it does not conform
to the ancestral system.

25:16.790 --> 25:17.880
Second,

25:17.880 --> 25:20.790
the throne is easily coveted.

25:26.640 --> 25:28.350
Passing His Majesty's oral decree:

25:28.350 --> 25:30.400
When I was ill,

25:30.590 --> 25:32.640
all ministers worked diligently

25:32.640 --> 25:34.170
and exhausted their minds.

25:34.200 --> 25:35.750
You are all meritorious.

25:35.960 --> 25:36.640
Today,

25:36.640 --> 25:39.160
I decide to open the treasury

25:39.160 --> 25:41.920
and grant all ministers 3 years' salary.

25:42.160 --> 25:43.640
By Imperial Command.

25:47.480 --> 25:50.160
We obey Your Majesty's edict.

25:50.160 --> 25:54.400
Long live Your Majesty.

25:57.070 --> 25:58.030
My ministers,

25:58.480 --> 25:59.440
you may rise.

26:00.750 --> 26:03.200
Thank you, Your Majesty.

26:08.640 --> 26:09.830
Your Majesty,

26:09.830 --> 26:12.270
this seems a bit inappropriate.

26:12.480 --> 26:15.270
As long as Your Majesty returns safely.

26:15.480 --> 26:16.720
This reward

26:16.720 --> 26:19.070
is quite a large expense.

26:19.070 --> 26:20.000
Lord Zhang.

26:20.240 --> 26:23.350
What's wrong with His Majesty
rewarding loyal subjects?

26:23.350 --> 26:25.440
Besides, you're also a loyal subject.

26:25.440 --> 26:26.240
His Majesty

26:26.440 --> 26:28.070
will also reward you.

26:28.880 --> 26:31.880
Please see clearly, Your Majesty.

26:32.480 --> 26:35.880
Zhang Ruizhong
is no loyal subject, either,

26:35.880 --> 26:36.830
Your Majesty.

26:36.830 --> 26:37.680
Lord Li,

26:38.160 --> 26:40.590
what nonsense are you talking about?

26:40.590 --> 26:41.520
Zhang Ruizhong,

26:41.550 --> 26:43.440
don't play dumb with me.

26:43.440 --> 26:43.880
You—

26:44.070 --> 26:45.200
Your Majesty,

26:45.350 --> 26:48.270
he has a dragon robe hidden in his house.

26:48.440 --> 26:51.640
He has long harbored the intention
to usurp the throne,

26:51.640 --> 26:54.270
Your Majesty.

26:54.270 --> 26:55.070
Xiao Chi.

26:55.550 --> 26:56.240
I am here.

26:56.480 --> 26:57.310
Investigate.

26:57.720 --> 26:58.850
I accept the decree.

27:07.590 --> 27:09.120
What else do you have to say?

27:09.270 --> 27:10.270
Your Majesty,

27:10.270 --> 27:13.030
I have truly never seen this thing before.

27:13.070 --> 27:15.070
I really haven't seen it.

27:15.070 --> 27:15.920
Lord Zhang.

27:16.270 --> 27:18.030
I searched this out myself.

27:18.070 --> 27:20.000
How could I be wronging you?

27:20.000 --> 27:21.160
General Xiao.

27:21.350 --> 27:23.200
How is this possible?

27:24.030 --> 27:27.070
These books are the sole surviving copies

27:27.070 --> 27:29.400
of ancient texts from various dynasties.

27:30.000 --> 27:30.880
Your Majesty.

27:30.880 --> 27:33.070
Years ago, I went
to Lord Zhang's house for his birthday.

27:33.070 --> 27:34.030
He got drunk

27:34.030 --> 27:36.240
and said he had a dragon robe hidden.

27:36.240 --> 27:38.750
He also said that one day
he would wear it,

27:38.750 --> 27:39.750
sit on the dragon throne,

27:39.750 --> 27:41.280
and lead the army in person.

27:41.640 --> 27:44.480
At the time, I thought he was just drunk

27:44.480 --> 27:45.550
and speaking happily—

27:45.550 --> 27:46.480
I thought that's just a jest
made under the influence of wine.

27:46.480 --> 27:47.400
Who would have thought

27:47.400 --> 27:48.240
he really had

27:48.240 --> 27:50.640
the intention to usurp
the throne, Your Majesty.

27:50.640 --> 27:51.640
Li Shichang!

27:51.640 --> 27:53.480
What nonsense are you talking about?

27:53.480 --> 27:54.880
Nonsense?

27:54.880 --> 27:55.680
Looking at it this way,

27:55.680 --> 27:57.350
who's behind His Majesty’s illness

27:57.350 --> 27:59.000
is still unknown.

27:59.000 --> 28:00.270
Your Majesty.

28:00.400 --> 28:02.680
Li Shichang is framing me!

28:02.680 --> 28:04.440
He is really framing me!

28:04.440 --> 28:06.240
Please see clearly, Your Majesty.

28:06.240 --> 28:09.160
Li Shichang, you bastard!

28:09.880 --> 28:10.830
Zhang Ruizhong.

28:10.830 --> 28:12.070
Words are not proof.

28:12.480 --> 28:14.550
This dragon robe is ironclad evidence,

28:14.550 --> 28:16.440
Your Majesty!

28:16.440 --> 28:17.880
I am innocent!

28:17.880 --> 28:19.110
I am innocent!

28:19.110 --> 28:20.040
Zhang Ruizhong!

28:21.640 --> 28:23.030
As the Chief Minister,

28:24.030 --> 28:26.430
I should have executed your entire family.

28:27.270 --> 28:30.470
But considering you assisted
the late Emperor for years,

28:30.640 --> 28:32.270
I will spare your life.

28:32.790 --> 28:33.510
From now on,

28:34.550 --> 28:36.000
you are grounded at home

28:36.000 --> 28:37.270
and must never leave!

28:37.400 --> 28:38.550
As for your family,

28:39.070 --> 28:40.750
they shall all be beheaded!

28:41.440 --> 28:44.160
I am innocent, Your Majesty!

28:44.160 --> 28:46.750
Your Majesty, I am innocent!

28:47.790 --> 28:48.790
Your Majesty.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.790
Your Majesty!

28:50.790 --> 28:52.960
Your Majesty!

28:52.960 --> 28:54.400
I am innocent!

28:54.400 --> 28:56.350
I am innocent!

28:56.350 --> 28:57.680
Your Majesty.

28:58.270 --> 29:02.030
I am innocent!

29:17.480 --> 29:18.880
Why do I have no appetite?

29:31.640 --> 29:32.880
You're all right.

29:33.880 --> 29:36.640
I thought you would never come back.

29:37.200 --> 29:38.790
During the time you were unconscious,

29:38.790 --> 29:40.350
I kept praying,

29:40.350 --> 29:43.270
wishing to exchange my life for yours.

29:48.160 --> 29:49.680
Now that I'm better,

29:50.640 --> 29:52.440
do you have to pay with your life?

29:58.270 --> 29:59.270
I'm kidding.

30:00.680 --> 30:01.640
Here I am,

30:01.880 --> 30:04.480
standing right in front of you,
alive and well.

30:04.480 --> 30:05.350
Don't worry.

30:06.270 --> 30:07.030
Come,

30:07.440 --> 30:08.500
let's have a drink.

30:11.960 --> 30:13.000
Somebody!

30:13.750 --> 30:14.680
Bring some wine.

30:21.480 --> 30:22.550
Your Majesty,

30:23.480 --> 30:24.240
I am pregnant.

30:24.240 --> 30:25.270
I cannot drink.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.480
Just a little bit.

30:28.240 --> 30:29.500
It won't hurt the baby.

30:30.880 --> 30:31.920
Besides,

30:32.400 --> 30:33.590
I just love drinking.

30:33.590 --> 30:35.200
If it is really my child,

30:36.200 --> 30:36.830
then...

30:37.480 --> 30:39.350
he should have liked drinking even

30:39.350 --> 30:41.070
when he was in the womb.

30:52.480 --> 30:54.340
Aren't you going to say something

30:55.480 --> 30:56.790
to congratulate me?

31:02.640 --> 31:04.240
I congratulate Your Majesty

31:04.880 --> 31:06.070
on your safe return.

31:07.030 --> 31:07.880
Good.

31:20.590 --> 31:21.440
My love,

31:21.880 --> 31:24.010
there is one thing I cannot figure out.

31:24.550 --> 31:25.350
Tell me,

31:26.000 --> 31:27.960
how did I get poisoned?

31:30.400 --> 31:31.480
I don't know.

31:31.830 --> 31:32.750
You don't know?

31:35.400 --> 31:36.640
I really don't know.

31:45.830 --> 31:47.590
Look me in the eye

31:48.160 --> 31:49.480
and say it again.

31:50.640 --> 31:51.790
I don't know.

31:52.070 --> 31:54.480
Is it possible that the food paid

31:55.830 --> 31:58.030
as tribute by Changmo was poisoned?

31:59.400 --> 32:00.510
You gave me all the foods

32:00.510 --> 32:02.480
that Changmo tributed.

32:02.640 --> 32:03.830
If anyone were to be poisoned,

32:03.830 --> 32:06.290
I would have been the first
to show symptoms.

32:07.830 --> 32:08.890
Then let me ask you.

32:09.880 --> 32:10.720
That string of

32:11.030 --> 32:12.440
Zhuyao...
